sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant System
    participant Database

    User->>System: Send Request
    activate System
    System->>Database: Query Data
    activate Database
    Database-->>System: Return Results
    deactivate Database
    System-->>User: Send Response
    deactivate System

    Note right of System: Process request
    Note over User,Database: End-to-end interaction

